summary: This new code file, moviepage10.html, contributes to the system by providing a webpage for a specific movie titled "Prehistoric Planet." It includes a poster image, a video embed, a summary of the movie, and a rating box where users can rate the movie. The file also introduces a hamburger menu for navigation and includes links to the home, about, and contact pages. The rating box allows users to submit their ratings for the movie, which are then displayed on the webpage. Overall, this file adds interactivity and user engagement features to the system.
